    <h1>Solr Search Engine Bundle</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p class=3D"confluence-link"><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozeng=
e aui-lozenge-current">5.4.X &gt;=3D 5.4.5</span></p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-war=
ning">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-error confluence-inform=
ation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>Support for Solr Search Engine Bundle when used in eZ Publish 5.4 with l=
egacy is limited, as the legacy integration is done by Netgen's <a href=3D"=
https://github.com/netgen/ezplatformsearch" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"=
nofollow">ezplatformsearch</a>, a third party community-supported extension=
.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p class=3D"confluence-link">For instructions on the bundle for eZ Platform=
, see <a href=3D"/display/EZP/Solr+Search+Engine+Bundle">Solr Search Engine=
 Bundle in the eZ Platform Developer documentation</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p><span>Version 1.0.x of Solr Bundle primarily aims to be drop in replacem=
ent for Legacy (SQL based) search engine for better scalability and perform=
ance <em>(mainly with field criteria and sort clauses).</em> And while it a=
lso provides better full text search thanks to Solr, more advance search fe=
atures like Faceting, Spellchecking, plugin system, .. will come in later r=
eleases, most for for newer versions of eZ Platform only. See <a href=3D"/d=
isplay/EZP/5.4.5+Release+Notes">5.4.5 Release Notes</a> for further info.</=
span></p>
